node.text:
As someone who has invested their time heavily within the automotive industry, working with some of the worlds most respected automotive brands, having the right tools is imperative. When @djiglobal came to me with their latest #Air2S it felt like the perfect fit. A compact, powerful drone with superior image quality, housed in a sturdy (and dust proof haha) casing. 

My assignment, at the time of coming up with a concept for #DJI, was for Bentley and their Flying Spur V8 — I couldn’t think of a better way to test the capabilities of DJI’s newest drone by pairing it with one of 2021’s most luxury cars.

node.text: Taking it back to my origin story as a photographer. When @LUMIXUK reached out with the challenge of capturing light with their new S5 camera, I knew I needed to go back to my roots and spend a night exploring the city as a way to reignite my passion. With features like its dual image stabilisation, incredible video specs, and dual native ISO technology, capturing the light in LA has me more excited than ever to be creating. Let me know what you think of the film and camera in the comments! #LUMIXS5 #ad #MovingImagesForward

node.text: Wanna spice up 2021? @theyachtweek just released their yachts for your 2021 European sailing adventure with bookings opening on the 8th Oct. Myself and the squad are ready to lock ours in for next year so what are you waiting for?! With the struggles of 2020 making our travel limited and ruining holidays, I know that many are looking at 2021 to be the opportunity to finally get away. If you want a week of sunshine, fun, dancing and exploring  then @theyachtweek literally ticks all those boxes and so much more. Hit up their Instagram to find out more. Video by the legendary @a.r.visual 😨

node.text:
These 4 pieces are currently being auctioned off to close out my “WORLD WONDERS” NFT series on @opensea — a total of 50 1/1 images which sold out in less than a minute. I’ve worked tirelessly within the NFT space this year, it has taken over much of my career and I’ve loved every second of growth that has come from it. It’s seen me make it into the all time top 30 most selling artists on @superrare.co while building incredible relationships with artists and collectors. I’ve been fortunate to learn and develop new skills and sell my work to collectors who truly value what I do. There’s been huge ups and downs throughout this time but I couldn’t be more stoked on where this journey is taking me. Thank you @aggie for your constant support, I couldn’t do this without you. 

There’s currently 10-15 minutes left on these 4 auctions, you can find them on opensea under “World Wonders By Jacob Riglin” 🤍🌎✈️

What better way to celebrate, than reminiscing and re-editing the photos we captured together during the first week we met! ❤️
